    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Well-kept older car in good overall condition and a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable driver-quality example. It presents nicely inside and out, appears complete, and shows the kind of normal age-related wear you would expect from a car that has been used and maintained rather than stored away as a showpiece. A buyer should expect a car that looks good, runs well, and can be enjoyed as-is, with the understanding that it is not a mint, concours-level example.",
