    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Solid, honest driver with plenty to like for someone seeking an affordable classic without project-car territory. This car is in fair overall condition: it presents decently, runs and drives, and should be enjoyable as-is while leaving room for cosmetic improvement and ongoing sorting typical of an older vehicle. Expect visible wear, age-related blemishes, and some imperfections throughout, but it has good potential for the next owner to tidy up and enjoy.",
