    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Outstanding mint-condition classic that shows beautifully and is the kind of car that really stands out for all the right reasons. It presents exceptionally well inside and out, has the sort of fit, finish, and overall freshness buyers hope to find, and is ready to be enjoyed, shown, or added to a serious collection. If you\u2019ve been waiting for a truly top-tier example without stepping into over-the-top pricing, this is a fantastic find.",
