    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Project car / rough driver being sold honestly as a poor-condition example. This car needs significant work and should be approached as a restoration candidate, parts car, or major project rather than something ready to enjoy right away. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear throughout, including tired paint, body flaws, aged trim, and an interior that shows heavy use. It should also be assumed to need mechanical attention, recommissioning, and general sorting before regular road use. Best suited for a buyer who knows what they are taking on and wants a car priced accordingly.",
